title: Antyjuan Rodriguez
text:
Antyjuan Rodriguez 
Position: ATH
Height/Weight: 6-1, 215
High School: Winter Springs
247Sports.com composite star rating : N/A
247Sports.com composite national ranking : N/A
247Sports.com position ranking : N/A
247Sports.com state ranking : N/A
Sentinel Central Florida Super60: No. 36
 
The buzz : Rodriguez has been a key figure on offense and defense for the Bears since his freshman season. A gifted athlete, he has been used at numerous positions during his career, including defensive back, linebacker, receiver, running back and kick returner. Heâ€™s one of the most gifted athletes in Central Florida and a college somewhere will be happy to get him.

Caption Video: Where's Coach Saban? Where's Dabo? Alabama, Clemson coaches lost amid title game chaos Alabama head coach Nick Saban and Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney, could not find each other for the customary postgame handshake following the College Football Playoff National Championship game in Tampa. The two good friends did eventually meet on the field following Clemson's 35-31 victory. (Swinney video by Chris Hays/Orlando Sentinel; Saban video by SEC Country; Photo by Getty Images)
